crystal_doc_search_index_callback({"repository_name":"downloader","body":"# downloader\n\n[![GitHub release](https://img.shields.io/github/release/gxfr/downloader.svg)](https://github.com/gxfr/downloader/releases)\n\nEasy way to download files via Crystal.\n\n## Installation\n\n1. Add the dependency to your `shard.yml`:\n\n   ```yaml\n   dependencies:\n     downloader:\n       github: gxfr/downloader\n   ```\n\n2. Run `shards install`\n\n## Usage\n\n```crystal\nrequire \"downloader\"\n```\n\nDownload a file:\n\n```crystal\nurl = \"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/88042940?v=4\"\nfilename = \"avatar.png\"\nDownloader.download(url, filename)\n```\n\n## Contributing\n\n1. Fork it (<https://github.com/gxfr/downloader>)\n2. Create your feature branch (`git checkout -b my-new-feature`)\n3. Commit your changes (`git commit -am 'Add some feature'`)\n4. Push to the branch (`git push origin my-new-feature`)\n5. Create a new Pull Request\n\n## Contributors\n\n- [gxfr](https://github.com/gxfr) - creator and maintainer\n","program":{"html_id":"downloader/toplevel","path":"toplevel.html","kind":"module","full_name":"Top Level Namespace","name":"Top Level Namespace","abstract":false,"locations":[],"repository_name":"downloader","program":true,"enum":false,"alias":false,"const":false,"types":[{"html_id":"downloader/Downloader","path":"Downloader.html","kind":"module","full_name":"Downloader","name":"Downloader","abstract":false,"locations":[{"filename":"src/downloader.cr","line_number":3,"url":"https://github.com/crystal-libs/downloader/blob/ba3828c837c1fa50bfd0b24e49ddbf2f331e5701/src/downloader.cr#L3"}],"repository_name":"downloader","program":false,"enum":false,"alias":false,"const":false,"constants":[{"id":"VERSION","name":"VERSION","value":"\"0.1.0\""}],"class_methods":[{"html_id":"download(url:String,filename:String)-class-method","name":"download","abstract":false,"args":[{"name":"url","external_name":"url","restriction":"String"},{"name":"filename","external_name":"filename","restriction":"String"}],"args_string":"(url : String, filename : String)","args_html":"(url : String, filename : String)","location":{"filename":"src/downloader.cr","line_number":6,"url":"https://github.com/crystal-libs/downloader/blob/ba3828c837c1fa50bfd0b24e49ddbf2f331e5701/src/downloader.cr#L6"},"def":{"name":"download","args":[{"name":"url","external_name":"url","restriction":"String"},{"name":"filename","external_name":"filename","restriction":"String"}],"visibility":"Public","body":"@@url = url\n@@filename = filename\nHTTP::Client.get(url) do |response|\n  if response.status_code == 200\n    File.write(filename, response.body_io)\n  else\n    raise(Exception.new(\"Unable To Download File: #{response.status_code} Status Code\"))\n  end\nend\n"}}]}]}})